channel.title: Problem with Cheezscape
channel.description:
I am using Cheezscape Update 80. I have found that I cannot sell anything to the general stores. I know that in shops.cfg it should have Buy 1 Sell 1, Which is there.
I changed it to Buy 2 Sell 2, Nothing, I can't even sell items that I buy off the shop back to it. So i changed it back and still nothing.
A little help please... Thanks.
